beer.beer_description: Boatrocker Beer Garden Pilsner is a New World Pilsner. It's our little nod to the amazing pilsners from Northern Germany...with a little love from New Zealand hops. We crafted this beer with only the best German pilsner malt, then loaded it up with some choice Kiwi hops (including late boil hop bursting & dry hopping).
